trans-unit.source: The StripLinesCollection class represents a collection of <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.StripLine> objects, and is implemented as the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis.StripLines%2A> property of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis> class.
trans-unit.target: A classe StripLinesCollection representa uma coleção de <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.StripLine>objetos e é implementado como a <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis.StripLines%2A>propriedade de <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis>classe.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis.StripLines%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.StripLine>

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.StripLine> objects can be appended, inserted or removed from the collection at both design time and run time.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.StripLine>objetos podem ser anexados, inseridos ou removidos da coleção em tempo de design e tempo de execução.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.StripLine>

trans-unit.source: **Note** Strip lines can be displayed once or repeatedly for a set interval.
trans-unit.target: **Observação** faixas podem ser exibidas uma vez ou repetidamente para um intervalo definido.
